<%- include('partials/header') %>

<section class="hero" style="padding-bottom: 2em;">
  <div class="container" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr;">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <span class="eyebrow">Legal</span>
      <h1>Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        These terms apply whenever you book a cab with Eva Tours and Travels,
        by phone, WhatsApp, or through this website.
      </p>
      <p style="font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.82rem; color: var(--ink-soft);">
        Last updated: July 2026
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="card" style="max-width: 820px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2.2em;">

      <h2>1. About These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        Eva Tours and Travels is a taxi service owned and operated by
        <%= business.owner %>, serving <%= business.location %> and
        surrounding routes. By calling to book a cab, submitting the
        booking form on this website, or taking a ride with us, you agree
        to the terms below.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Bookings</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Bookings can be made by phone, WhatsApp, or through the contact form on this website.</li>
        <li>A booking is confirmed only once our team calls back to confirm the vehicle, timing and fare.</li>
        <li>For outstation, airport, and rental packages, the fare is agreed upfront before the trip begins.</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to decline a booking if a suitable vehicle or driver is not available for the requested time.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. Fares &amp; Payment</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Local rides are charged as per the agreed package or on-call quote; outstation and rental fares are fixed before departure.</li>
        <li>Tolls, parking, state permits, and interstate taxes (where applicable) are charged extra unless stated otherwise at the time of booking.</li>
        <li>Payment is collected by the driver at the end of the trip, by cash or UPI, unless a different arrangement is agreed in advance.</li>
        <li>Waiting time beyond what was agreed at booking may be charged additionally, as informed by the driver or our booking line.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Cancellations &amp; Changes</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You may cancel or reschedule a booking by calling us as early as possible before the pickup time.</li>
        <li>Last-minute cancellations, especially for outstation and airport bookings where a driver has already been dispatched, may attract a cancellation charge — this will be communicated at the time of booking.</li>
        <li>We will inform you as early as possible if we need to reassign your driver or vehicle due to unforeseen circumstances.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Passenger Conduct &amp; Luggage</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Passengers are responsible for their own luggage and belongings; please check the vehicle before ending your trip.</li>
        <li>We ask passengers to treat drivers and vehicles with courtesy. The driver may decline to continue a trip in case of abusive behaviour or unsafe conduct.</li>
        <li>Smoking is not permitted inside the vehicle. Additional cleaning charges may apply for any damage or mess caused during a trip.</li>
        <li>Vehicle capacity (seats and luggage) is fixed per vehicle type — please share accurate passenger and luggage details at the time of booking.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. Driver &amp; Vehicle Standards</h2>
      <p>
        We assign licensed drivers and maintain our vehicles for regular
        upkeep. If you have any concern about a driver or vehicle during
        or after a trip, please report it to us directly using the
        contact details below so we can look into it.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Liability</h2>
      <p>
        Eva Tours and Travels takes reasonable care to ensure safe and
        timely travel, but is not liable for delays caused by traffic,
        weather, road closures, or other circumstances beyond our
        control. We are not responsible for items left behind in the
        vehicle, though we will make reasonable efforts to help recover
        them if reported promptly.
      </p>

      <h2>8. Website Use</h2>
      <p>
        This website is provided to help you learn about our services and
        submit booking enquiries. Package rates shown on the
        <a href="/packages">Packages page</a> are indicative starting
        rates and are always confirmed on call before a booking is
        finalised. We may update page content, including rates and
        service details, at any time without prior notice.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>
        We may revise these terms from time to time as our services
        change. The "Last updated" date at the top of this page reflects
        the most recent revision. Continuing to book with us after
        changes are posted means you accept the updated terms.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Governing Law</h2>
      <p>
        These terms are governed by the laws of India, and any disputes
        will be subject to the jurisdiction of the courts in Pune,
        Maharashtra.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        For any questions about these terms, reach out to
        <%= business.owner %> directly:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Phone: <a href="tel:+91<%= business.phone1 %>"><%= business.phone1 %></a> / <a href="tel:+91<%= business.phone2 %>"><%= business.phone2 %></a></li>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:<%= business.email %>"><%= business.email %></a></li>
        <li>Service area: <%= business.location %></li>
      </ul>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section-ink">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <h2>Ready to book?</h2>
    <p>Call us and we'll confirm your fare before you travel.</p>
    <a href="tel:+91<%= business.phone1 %>" class="btn btn-primary"><%= business.phone1 %></a>
  </div>
</section>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>